(Camera) '
() '
(See everything. Miss nothing.) '
() '
(The 48MP Fusion camera captures extraordinary detail in every shot. The 5x Telephoto) '
(brings far subjects close without losing sharpness. And for the first time, Cinematic mode) '
(shoots in 4K at 120 frames per second   giving you a tool that belongs on a film set, in a) '
(device that fits in your pocket.) '
() '
(---) '
() '
(Apple Intelligence) '
() '
(It understands you.) '
() '
(Apple Intelligence is built into the apps you use every day. It helps you write with) '
(greater clarity, find exactly what you're looking for across all your content, and handle) '
(the things that used to slow you down. It knows your context. It respects your privacy.) '
(And it gets better the more you use it.) '
() '
(---) '
