(M4 Chip) '
() '
(Performance on a different level.) '
() '
(M4 is the most powerful chip ever put into a mainstream product. The 10-core CPU handles) '
(demanding tasks without breaking a sweat. The 10-core GPU brings desktop-class graphics to) '
(a device you can carry anywhere. And the 16-core Neural Engine runs Apple Intelligence at) '
(a speed that makes it feel instant.) '
() '
(---) '
() '
(Privacy) '
() '
(Your data. Your device. Your call.) '
() '
(Privacy isn't a feature. It's the foundation. On-device processing means your personal) '
(information stays with you. When Apple Intelligence needs to go further, Private Cloud) '
(Compute sends only what's necessary   and only to servers that never store your data.) '
(Verified independently. Built into everything you use.) '
() '
(---) '
() '
(Continuity) '
() '
(All your devices. One experience.) '
() '
(Pick up exactly where you left off, on any device. Copy on your iPhone, paste on your Mac.) '
(Take a call on your iPad, hand it off to your iPhone as you walk out the door. Your Apple) '
(devices don't just work together. They work as one.) '
